Kingsley
Abasili who has been described as Pete Edochie’s look-alike has
officially joined the local movie industry to begin his career.  Kingsley Abasili and Pete Edochie   Do you remember Kingsley Abasili who is popularly known as Pete Edochie’s look-alike?   He has found his way to Nollywood and featured in a Nollywood movie. He was spotted on a movie set with Gentle Jack, Labistar and other Nollywood stars.    He might look like the veteran actor who has spent decades in the industry but he doesn’t match him as par acting skills and experience. See more pictures below: (Tori.ng)